  "browser_support": "All modern browsers. The pure-CSS version needs a known character count and a monospace font.",
  "performance_notes": "Animating width triggers layout but on a single short line it is negligible.",
  "accessibility_notes": "Full text is present in the DOM immediately (just visually clipped), so screen readers get it. Animation is skipped under prefers-reduced-motion (text shown instantly).",
